  "name": "RPlog_Farewell_Qwynt",
  "title": "Farewell, Qwynt",
  "summary": "A galaxy of mourners, opportunists, and hangers-on gathers at Smitherbodkins Manor for the chaotic funeral of the Amalgamated Waste kingpin G.S. Qwynt III. The grief-stricken Ortolan Frederiko, named the deceased's benefactor, weeps theatrically and invites everyone to shout their feelings at Qwynt's giant portrait, while the manor's host Smitherbodkins struggles to keep the proceedings appropriate and the Verpine Murdock secretly slices the building's systems to engineer a moment of silence by cutting all power. The Qwynt family arrives in force, led by the morbidly obese Momma Cleo on a repulsorsled and her sons Poot, Boo-T, and Tiny, while two rival 'fiances' brawl in the lovers' section. Imperial officers including Commander Dante and Warlord Korolov look on with concealed amusement and mounting irritation, Dante even using the blackout to swap seats and dodge the smitten Poot. After Smitherbodkins delivers a hollow eulogy and assures Momma her son died with her name on his lips, the service dissolves into a meat-snack reception, drinking contests, and running children before the guests trickle out.",
